rComments: The best prof I have ever had! She summarized all the readings in her slides making it very easy to know the important parts. Assignments were easy and midterm and exam very fair all based on lecture mainly. The most understanding and kind professor ive ever had I would take any class she ever teaches. 1000000% recommend her any of her classes

I went to her office hours many times. We had agreed upon re-submitting an assignment and she made no changes to my mark even though I had made all the changes she insisted upon. I made an account just for this professor because I was tricked into getting a terrible final grade. An overwhelming amount of work, and she didn't keep her word.
